            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英皇國際港島南現樓臨海住宅項目「澄天」周末再錄得成交",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英皇國際港島南現樓臨海住宅項目「澄天」繼日前沽出三伙兩房戶後，周末再度錄得成交，項目本月累計共售出四伙單位，僅八天已套現近$2,700萬元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"英皇國際港島南現樓臨海住宅項目「澄天」。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250308_CR_Source-web_Sky_01.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"英皇國際港島南現樓臨海住宅項目「澄天」。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250308_CR_Source-web_Sky_01.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">英皇國際港島南現樓臨海住宅項目「澄天」。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今日售出單位為11樓E室，實用面積286平方呎，成交價$483.94萬元，成交呎價$16,921，屬一房戶型。買家為本地年輕才俊，鑑於一房單位開則實用、佈局靈活、且交通便利方便上班，十分適合未來新婚之用，故火速購入單位自用。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「澄天」至今已售出89伙，佔整體項目81%，共套現逾5.56億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14762507-%e8%8b%b1%e7%9a%87%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e6%b8%af%e5%b3%b6%e5%8d%97%e7%8f%be%e6%a8%93%e8%87%a8%e6%b5%b7%e4%bd%8f%e5%ae%85%e9%a0%85%e7%9b%ae%e3%80%8c%e6%be%84%e5%a4%a9%e3%80%8d%e5%91%a8%e6%9c%ab%e5%86%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250308_CR_Source-web_Sky_02.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 17:00:55",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "舜宇上月手機鏡頭出貨量按年降6.9% 手機攝像模組跌32.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">舜宇光學(02382)公布，今年2月份手機鏡頭出貨量9716.8萬件，按年減少6.9%，按月也降8.2%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學2023年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240422_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：舜宇光學2023年度年報封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240422_FI_source-web_02382.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：舜宇光學2023年度年報封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內車載鏡頭出貨量881.1萬件，按年升12.9%，按月降31.3%，主要因為12月份聖誕節假期使得1月份集中出貨，導致1月份出貨量基數較高；玻璃球面鏡片130.6萬件，按年升18.4%，按月減少47.1%；其他鏡頭667.5萬件，按年增15.5%，按年減少42.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">手機攝像模組上月出貨量3537.1萬件，按年減少32.1%，主要因為公司更多專注於中高端案子，且產品結構較去年同期改善，出貨量按月只降3.8%。其他光電產品出貨量260.6萬件，按年升34.3%，按月降11.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">顯微儀器上月出貨量1828.4萬件，按年增1.33倍，按月減少23.9%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14766063-%e8%88%9c%e5%ae%87%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f%e9%8f%a1%e9%a0%ad%e5%87%ba%e8%b2%a8%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d6-9-%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f%e6%94%9d%e5%83%8f%e6%a8%a1%e7%b5%84%e8%b7%8c32-1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/02382-Web2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 17:00:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "香港中旅料去年純利跌最少40%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">香港中旅(00308)發盈警，預期2024年度純利按年倒退不少於40%，主要受投資物業公允價下跌影響。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14766049-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e4%b8%ad%e6%97%85%e6%96%99%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c%e6%9c%80%e5%b0%9140",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20230831_FI_source-web_00308_CHINA-TRAVEL_FB.jpg.webp",
