        {
            "title": "零跑上季虧轉盈 去年經調整淨虧損收窄至23.5億元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">零跑汽車(09863)公布，提前1年於2024年第4季實現淨利潤轉正的目標；2024年經調整淨虧損亦收窄至23.5億元(人民幣．下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：零跑汽車官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230825_FI_source-web_零跑汽車2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：零跑汽車官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230825_FI_source-web_零跑汽車2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：零跑汽車官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司表示，上季實現淨利潤8000萬元，毛利率13.3%，創成立以來新高。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於2024年度全年，該公司收益321.6億元，按年升92%；汽車總交付量29.37萬輛，按年也升1.04倍，成為期內交付量增長最快的造車新勢力品牌，全年銷量在造車新劫力品牌銷量榜也穩居前三之列。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">零跑於2024年毛利率達8.4%，按年提升7.9個百分點。公司權益持有人應佔淨虧損28.2億元，虧損按年收窄14億元或33.2%；按非國際財報告準則的經調整淨虧損23.5億元，按年收窄11.7億元或33.2%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司去年從經營活動產生金淨額84.7億元，按年大升6.84倍；自由現金流由負轉正，達63.2億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14766008-%e9%9b%b6%e8%b7%91%e4%b8%8a%e5%ad%a3%e8%99%a7%e8%bd%89%e7%9b%88-%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b6%93%e8%aa%bf%e6%95%b4%e6%b7%a8%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84%e8%87%b323-5%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230825_FI_source-web_09863.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 16:50:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股收跌447點   晶片股消費股全日捱沽",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股全日收跌447點，午後跌破上午低位，臨近尾段跌幅略收窄，晶片股及消費股全日捱沽，龍頭科網股推低大市，航運股逆市升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日報23783，跌447點或1.85 %，今早開市報24115點，跌115點或0.48%，一度見24292，升61點或0.25%，隨即拾級而下，午後跌破上午低位，低見23632，瀉599點或2.47%，為全日低位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：奈雪的茶官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240718_FI_source-web_02150-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：奈雪的茶官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240718_FI_source-web_02150-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：奈雪的茶官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230718-135126_source-web_00241-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230718-135126_source-web_00241-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里健康官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：東方海外官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240104_FI_source-web_oocl.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：東方海外官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240104_FI_source-web_oocl.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：東方海外官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：奈雪的茶官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240718_FI_source-web_02150-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：奈雪的茶官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230718-135126_source-web_00241-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里健康官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：東方海外官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240104_FI_source-web_oocl.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：東方海外官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日報5885，跌151點或2.52%，今早開報6016點，跌21點或0.35%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報8725，跌189點或2.12%，今早以8873點開市，跌40點或0.45%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指全日跌480點或1.98%，報23758，低水25點 ; 科指期貨半日跌161點或2.67%，報5876點，低水9點 ; 國指期貨跌194點或2.18%，報8722，低水3點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地公布2月消費物價數據，2月CPI降0.7%，再陷通縮，且低於預期的0.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股大挫，中芯國際(00981)跌4.67%，報52.05元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 華虹半導體(01347)跌3.16%，報36.8元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">消費股捱沽，申洲國際(02313)收跌5.42%，報60.25元，跌幅藍籌股中居第二位 ;美團(03690)跌4.69%，報174.9元，李寧(02331)跌4.5%，報17.82元 ; 海底撈(06862)跌4.46%，報16.72元 ; 安踏(02020)跌2.09%，報96.15元 ; 華潤啤酒(00291)跌2.2%，報26.2元 ; 青島啤酒(00168)跌3.07%，報52.15元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">奈雪的茶(02150)全日收瀉20.73%，報1.3元，公司預期去年經調整轉蝕逾8.8億人民幣，同時遭調出深交所港股通標的證券名單。同被剔出「港股通」的海倫司(09869)收挫19.63%，報1.72元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：奈雪的茶官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240718_FI_source-web_02150-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：奈雪的茶官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240718_FI_source-web_02150-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：奈雪的茶官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中資電訊股弱，聯通(00762)挫4.94%，報9.43元 ; 中電信(00728)跌3.54%，報5.99元 ; 中移動(00941)跌0.54%，報83.1元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">龍頭科網股弱，成跌市元兇，阿里巴巴(09988)跌3.93%，報134.5元 ; 騰訊(00700)跌3.19%，報516.5元 ; 小米(01810)跌2.76%，報52.85元 ; 京東(09618)瀉4.59%，報162.3元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">網上醫療股逆升，阿里健康(00241)升3.26%，報5.71元，為表現最佳藍籌股 ; 平安好醫生()1833)升1.11%，報8.18元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230718-135126_source-web_00241-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里健康官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230718-135126_source-web_00241-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里健康官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">航運股上，東方海外(00316)升2.99%，報110.3元; 中遠海控(01919)升2.06%，報11.9元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">獲調入的方舟健客(06086)勁升40.72%，報6.22元；晶苑(02232)爆升12.8%，報5.64元 ; 同源康醫藥(02410)升16.18%，報35.55元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">被調出「港股通」名單的京基金融(01468)狂瀉34.4%，報0.246元；創新奇智(02121)挫27.73%，報4.17元；馬可數字科技跌27.16%，報0.59元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：東方海外官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240104_FI_source-web_oocl.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：東方海外官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240104_FI_source-web_oocl.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：東方海外官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14766030-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c447%e9%bb%9e-%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e8%82%a1%e6%b6%88%e8%b2%bb%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%8d%b1%e6%b2%bd",
